    "content" : "Once you start putting your floor in and building up your interior (bulkheads etc), you can make some space for a fuel tank by eating into the dead space behind the rear seat.\n<br> \n<br> One thing to consider is where your fuel filler neck is going to run, mine needs to go right where the chassis brace is... So going to have to go round it, which will make filling an arse.",
