    "content" : "Thanks for the tip elrao.\n<br> \n<br> Some more work today on the sub frame mounting points and the engine rails for the rear engine mount.\n<br> \n<br> \n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/TGJzBA\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/33935162788_95d696b291_k.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/TGJzBA\" class=\"postlink\">Rear Sub Frame</a> by \n<a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/78596025@N06/\" class=\"postlink\">Duke of Boots1966</a>, on Flickr\n<br> \n<br> \n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/S5tLPP\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/32868523197_25cc8d2fc8_z.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/S5tLPP\" class=\"postlink\">Rear Sub Frame</a> by \n<a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/78596025@N06/\" class=\"postlink\">Duke of Boots1966</a>, on Flickr\n<br> \n<br> \n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/2fLoY4b\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/47760094152_d6dcdc68a2_k.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/2fLoY4b\" class=\"postlink\">Rear Sub Frame</a> by \n<a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/78596025@N06/\" class=\"postlink\">Duke of Boots1966</a>, on Flickr\n<br> I have built the engine rail arms so they will pick up with there inner face of the rear wheel tub and i can put a few supporting welds along.\n<br> \n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/TGJzyE\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/33935162618_064496be16_z.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/TGJzyE\" class=\"postlink\">Rear Sub Frame</a> by \n<a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/78596025@N06/\" class=\"postlink\">Duke of Boots1966</a>, on Flickr\n<br> \n<br> \n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/25epexe\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/40845767183_3a7d63cb80_k.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/25epexe\" class=\"postlink\">Rear Sub Frame</a> by \n<a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/78596025@N06/\" class=\"postlink\">Duke of Boots1966</a>, on Flickr\n<br> \n<br> \n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/2fQZNPe\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/47812157971_f7718a6e5e_k.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/2fQZNPe\" class=\"postlink\">Engine Mount</a> by \n<a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/78596025@N06/\" class=\"postlink\">Duke of Boots1966</a>, on Flickr",
